nslation":"Tempat-Tempat Naik","num_ayah":44,"page":568,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5405,"surah_id":70,"ayah":30,"page":569,"quarter_hizb":57.75,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"arabic":"اِلَّا عَلٰٓى اَزْوَاجِهِمْ اَوْ مَا مَلَكَتْ اَيْمَانُهُمْ فَاِنَّهُمْ غَيْرُ مَلُوْمِيْنَۚ","kitabah":"اِلَّا عَلٰٓى اَزْوَاجِهِمْ اَوْ مَا مَلَكَتْ اَيْمَانُهُمْ فَاِنَّهُمْ غَيْرُ مَلُوْمِيْنَۚ","latin":"Illā ‘alā azwājihim au mā malakat aimānuhum fa innahum gairu malūmīn(a).","arabic_words":null,"translation":"kecuali terhadap istri-istri mereka atau hamba sahaya yang mereka miliki.724) Sesungguhnya mereka tidak tercela (karena menggaulinya).","footnotes":"724) Lihat catatan kaki surah al-Mu’minūn (23): 6.","updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":70,"arabic":" المعارج","latin":"Al-Ma‘ārij","transliteration":"Al-Ma‘arij","translation":"Tempat-Tempat Naik","num_ayah":44,"page":568,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5406,"surah_id":70,"ayah":31,"page":569,"quarter_hizb":57.75,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"arabic":"فَمَنِ ابْتَغٰى وَرَاۤءَ ذٰلِكَ فَاُولٰۤىِٕكَ هُمُ الْعَادُوْنَۚ","kitabah":"فَمَنِ ابْتَغٰى وَرَاۤءَ ذٰلِكَ فَاُولٰۤىِٕكَ هُمُ الْعَادُوْنَۚ","latin":"Fa manibtagā warā'a żālika fa ulā'ika  humul-‘ādūn(a).","arabic_words":null,"translation":"Maka, siapa yang mencari (pelampiasan syahwat) selain itu, mereka itulah orang-orang yang melampaui batas.","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":70,"arabic":" المعارج","latin":"Al-Ma‘ārij","transliteration":"Al-Ma‘arij","translation":"Tempat-Tempat Naik","num_ayah":44,"page":568,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5407,"surah_id":70,"ayah":32,"page":569,"quarter_hizb":57.75,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"arabic":"وَالَّذِيْنَ هُمْ لِاَمٰنٰتِهِمْ وَعَهْدِهِمْ رٰعُوْنَۖ","kitabah":"وَالَّذِيْنَ هُمْ لِاَمٰنٰتِهِمْ وَعَهْدِهِمْ رٰعُوْنَۖ","latin":"Wal-lażīna hum li'amānātihim wa ‘ahdihim rā'ūn(a).","arabic_words":null,"translation":"(Termasuk orang yang selamat dari azab adalah) orang-orang yang memelihara amanat dan janji mereka,","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":70,"arabic":" المعارج","latin":"Al-Ma‘ārij","transliteration":"Al-Ma‘arij","translation":"Tempat-Tempat Naik","num_ayah":44,"page":568,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5408,"surah_id":70,"ayah":33,"page":569,"quarter_hizb":57.75,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"arabic":"وَالَّذِيْنَ هُمْ بِشَهٰدٰتِهِمْ قَاۤىِٕمُوْنَۖ","kitabah":"وَالَّذِيْنَ هُمْ بِشَهٰدٰتِهِمْ قَاۤىِٕمُوْنَۖ","latin":"Wal-lażīna hum bisyahādātihim qā'imūn(a).","arabic_words":null,"translation":"yang memberikan kesaksiannya (secara benar),","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":70,"arabic":" المعارج","latin":"Al-Ma‘ārij","transliteration":"Al-Ma‘arij","translation":"Tempat-Tempat Naik","num_ayah":44,"page":568,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5409,"surah_id":70,"ayah":34,"page":569,"quarter_hizb":57.75,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"arabic":"وَالَّذِيْنَ هُمْ عَلٰى صَلَاتِهِمْ يُحَافِظُوْنَۖ","kitabah":"وَالَّذِيْنَ هُمْ عَلٰى صَلَاتِهِمْ يُحَافِظُوْنَۖ","latin":"Wal-lażīna hum ‘alā ṣalātihim yuḥāfiẓūn(a).","arabic_words":null,"translation":"dan yang memelihara salatnya.","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":70,"arabic":" المعارج","latin":"Al-Ma‘ārij","transliteration":"Al-Ma‘arij","translation":"Tempat-Tempat Naik","num_ayah":44,"page":568,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5410,"surah_id":70,"ayah":35,"page":569,"quarter_hizb":57.75,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"arabic":"اُولٰۤىِٕكَ فِيْ جَنّٰتٍ مُّكْرَمُوْنَ ۗ ࣖ","kitabah":"اُولٰۤىِٕكَ فِيْ جَنّٰتٍ مُّكْرَمُوْنَ ۗ ࣖ","latin":"Ulā'ika fī jannātim mukramūn(a).","arabic_words":null,"translation":"Mereka itu (berada) di surga lagi dimuliakan.","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":70,"arabic":" المعارج","latin":"Al-Ma‘ārij","transliteration":"Al-Ma‘arij","translation":"Tempat-Tempat Naik","num_ayah":44,"page":568,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5411,"surah_id":70,"ayah":36,"page":569,"quarter_hizb":57.75,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"arabic":"فَمَالِ الَّذِيْنَ كَفَرُوْا قِبَلَكَ مُهْطِعِيْنَۙ","kitabah":"فَمَالِ الَّذِيْنَ كَفَرُوْا قِبَلَكَ مُهْطِعِيْنَۙ","latin":"Famālil-lażīna kafarū qibalaka muhṭi‘īn(a).","arabic_words":null,"translation":"Mengapa orang-orang kafir itu bersegera datang ke arahmu (Nabi Muhammad)","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":70,"arabic":" المعارج","latin":"Al-Ma‘ārij","transliteration":"Al-Ma‘arij","translation":"Tempat-Tempat Naik","num_ayah":44,"page":568,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5412,"surah_id":70,"ayah":37,"page":569,"quarter_hizb":57.75,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"arabic":"عَنِ الْيَمِيْنِ وَعَنِ الشِّمَالِ عِزِيْنَ ","kitabah":"عَنِ الْيَمِيْنِ وَعَنِ الشِّمَالِ عِزِيْنَ ","latin":"‘Anil-yamīni wa ‘anisy-syimāli ‘izīn(a).","arabic_words":null,"translation":"dari kanan dan dari kiri dengan berkelompok-kelompok?725)","footnotes":"725) Menurut sebagian mufasir, padasuatu hari orang-orang musyrik berkerumun di hadapan Rasulullah saw. sambil mengejek dan mengatakan, “Jika orang-orang mukmin benar-benar akan masuk surga sebagaimana kata Muhammad, kitalah yang akan masuk terlebih dahulu.” Maka, turunlah ayat 38.","updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":70,"arabic":" المعارج","latin":"Al-Ma‘ārij","transliteration":"Al-Ma‘arij","translation":"Tempat-Tempat Naik","num_ayah":44,"page":568,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5413,"surah_id":70,"ayah":38,"page":569,"quarter_hizb":57.75,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"arabic":"اَيَطْمَعُ كُلُّ امْرِئٍ مِّنْهُمْ اَنْ يُّدْخَلَ جَنَّةَ نَعِيْمٍۙ","kitabah":"اَيَطْمَعُ كُلُّ امْرِئٍ مِّنْهُمْ اَنْ يُّدْخَلَ جَنَّةَ نَعِيْمٍۙ","latin":"Ayaṭma‘u kullumri'im minhum ay yudkhala jannata na‘īm(in).","arabic_words":null,"translation":"Apakah setiap orang dari mereka (orang-orang kafir itu) ingin dimasukkan ke dalam surga yang penuh kenikmatan?","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":70,"arabic":" المعارج","latin":"Al-Ma‘ārij","transliteration":"Al-Ma‘arij","translation":"Tempat-Tempat Naik","num_ayah":44,"page":568,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5414,"surah_id":70,"ayah":39,"page":569,"quarter_hizb":57.75,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"arabic":"كَلَّاۗ اِنَّا خَلَقْنٰهُمْ مِّمَّا يَعْلَمُوْنَ ","kitabah":"كَلَّاۗ اِنَّا خَلَقْنٰهُمْ مِّمَّا يَعْلَمُوْنَ ","latin":"Kallā, innā khalaqnāhum mimmā ya‘malūn(a).","arabic_words":null,"translation":"Sekali-kali tidak! Sesungguhnya Kami menciptakan mereka dari apa yang mereka ketahui (air mani).726)","footnotes":"726) Orang-orang kafir itu mengetahui bahwa mereka diciptakan oleh Allah dari air mani untuk beriman dan bertakwa kepada-Nya seperti manusia lainnya. Jadi, jika tidak beriman dan bertakwa, mereka tidak berhak masuk surga.","updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":70,"arabic":" المعارج","latin":"Al-Ma‘ārij","transliteration":"Al-Ma‘arij","translation":"Tempat-Tempat Naik","num_ayah":44,"page":568,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5415,"surah_id":70,"ayah":40,"page":570,"quarter_hizb":57.75,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"arabic":"فَلَآ اُقْسِمُ بِرَبِّ الْمَشٰرِقِ وَالْمَغٰرِبِ اِنَّا لَقٰدِرُوْنَۙ","kitabah":"فَلَآ اُقْسِمُ بِرَبِّ الْمَشٰرِقِ وَالْمَغٰرِبِ اِنَّا لَقٰدِرُوْنَۙ","latin":"Falā uqsimu birabbil-masyāriqi wal-magāribi  innā laqādirūn(a).","arabic_words":null,"translation":"Maka, Aku bersumpah dengan Tuhan yang mengatur tempat-tempat terbit dan terbenamnya (matahari, bulan, dan bintang), sesungguhnya Kami benar-benar Maha Kuasa","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":70,"arabic":" المعارج","latin":"Al-Ma‘ārij","transliteration":"Al-Ma‘arij","translation":"Tempat-Tempat Naik","num_ayah":44,"page":568,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5416,"surah_id":70,"ayah":41,"page":570,"quarter_hizb":57.75,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"arabic":"عَلٰٓى اَنْ نُّبَدِّلَ خَيْرًا مِّنْهُمْۙ وَمَا نَحْنُ بِمَسْبُوْقِيْنَ ","kitabah":"عَلٰٓى اَنْ نُّبَدِّلَ خَيْرًا مِّنْهُمْۙ وَمَا نَحْنُ بِمَسْبُوْقِيْنَ ","latin":"‘Alā an nubaddila khairam minhum, wa mā naḥnu bimasbūqīn(a).","arabic_words":null,"translation":"untuk mengganti (mereka) dengan (kaum) yang lebih baik daripada mereka. Kami sekali-kali tidak dapat dikalahkan.","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":70,"arabic":" المعارج","latin":"Al-Ma‘ārij","transliteration":"Al-Ma‘arij","translation":"Tempat-Tempat Naik","num_ayah":44,"page":568,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5417,"surah_id":70,"ayah":42,"page":570,"quarter_hizb":57.75,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"arabic":"فَذَرْهُمْ يَخُوْضُوْا وَيَلْعَبُوْا حَتّٰى يُلٰقُوْا يَوْمَهُمُ الَّذِيْ يُوْعَدُوْنَۙ","kitabah":"فَذَرْهُمْ يَخُوْضُوْا وَيَلْعَبُوْا حَتّٰى يُلٰقُوْا يَوْمَهُمُ الَّذِيْ يُوْعَدُوْنَۙ","latin":"Fa żarhum yakhūḍū  wa yal‘abū ḥattā yulāqū yaumahumul-lażī yū‘adūn(a)","arabic_words":null,"translation":"Maka, biarkanlah mereka tenggelam (dalam kesesatan) dan bermain-main (di dunia) sampai mereka menjumpai hari yang dijanjikan kepada mereka,","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":70,"arabic":" المعارج","latin":"Al-Ma‘ārij","transliteration":"Al-Ma‘arij","translation":"Tempat-Tempat Naik","num_ayah":44,"page":568,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5418,"surah_id":70,"ayah":43,"page":570,"quarter_hizb":57.75,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"arabic":"يَوْمَ يَخْرُجُوْنَ مِنَ الْاَجْدَاثِ سِرَاعًا كَاَنَّهُمْ اِلٰى نُصُبٍ يُّوْفِضُوْنَۙ","kitabah":"يَوْمَ يَخْرُجُوْنَ مِنَ الْاَجْدَاثِ سِرَاعًا كَاَنَّهُمْ اِلٰى نُصُبٍ يُّوْفِضُوْنَۙ","latin":"Yauma yakhrujūna minal-ajdāṡi sirā‘an ka'annahum ilā nuṣubiy yūfiḍūn(a).","arabic_words":null,"translation":"(yaitu) pada hari ketika mereka keluar dari kubur dengan cepat seperti ketika mereka pergi dengan segera menuju berhala-berhala (sewaktu di dunia).","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":70,"arabic":" المعارج","latin":"Al-Ma‘ārij","transliteration":"Al-Ma‘arij","translation":"Tempat-Tempat Naik","num_ayah":44,"page":568,"location":"Makkiyah"}},{"id":5419,"surah_id":70,"ayah":44,"page":570,"quarter_hizb":57.75,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"arabic":"خَاشِعَةً اَبْصَارُهُمْ تَرْهَقُهُمْ ذِلَّةٌ  ۗذٰلِكَ الْيَوْمُ الَّذِيْ كَانُوْا يُوْعَدُوْنَ ࣖ ","kitabah":"خَاشِعَةً اَبْصَارُهُمْ تَرْهَقُهُمْ ذِلَّةٌ  ۗذٰلِكَ الْيَوْمُ الَّذِيْ كَانُوْا يُوْعَدُوْنَ ࣖ ","latin":"Khāsyi‘atan abṣāruhum tarhaquhum żillah(tun), żālikal-yaumul-lażī kānū yū‘adūn(a).","arabic_words":null,"translation":"Pandangan mereka tertunduk (serta) diliputi kehinaan. Itulah hari yang diancamkan kepada mereka.","footnotes":null,"updated_at":null,"surah":{"id":70,"arabic":" المعارج","latin":"Al-Ma‘ārij","transliteration":"Al-Ma‘arij","translation":"Tempat-Tempat Naik","num_ayah":44,"page":568,"location":"Makkiyah"}}]}